<div class="col-md-9 col-xl-8">
  <main class="px-3">
    <h1 class="mt-5">Active Record Associations</h1>
    <p class="w-75">This article will help you understand <code>Active Record</code> and how to make <code>Associations</code>.</p>

    <p class="w-75"><code>Active Record</code> is, basically, the part of Rails that takes care of all the database stuff.
    It lets you work with your data models (ex. users, posts, comments, followers, etc.) in a nearly plain-English way.
    </p>

    <p class="w-75"><code>Associations</code> make a connection between two data models,
      which makes common database operations simpler and easier.
    </p>

